---
<MainLayout title="Programs" description="Explore Atma Bawana program areas.">
  <section class="bg-background py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center space-y-4">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-accent-innovator">Program Areas</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading">Where Guardians Act</h1>
      <p class="text-text/70">
        Each program moves through the cycle of protect, create, redeem â€” ensuring communities feel agency and hope.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-20 space-y-6">
    {programs.map((program) => (
      <article class="bg-white border border-accent-earth/60 rounded-3xl shadow-card p-8" key={program.title}>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-3 text-brand-green">{program.title}</h2>
        <p class="text-text/80 mb-4">{program.description}</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text/70 space-y-1">
          {program.activities.map((item) => (
            <li>{item}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </article>
    ))}
  </section>
</MainLayout>
